def: A kind of case shot for cannon, in which a number of lead oriron balls in layers are inclosed in a case fitting the gun; --called also canister shot,
The apparatus used in Marconi wireless telegraphy.
Capable of being replaced (by), or of being exchanged (for);as, the hydrogen of acids is replaceable by metals or by basicradicals.
Pertaining to, or used for, the determination of the amount ofozone; of or relating to ozonometry.
An avoiding or escaping; also, a warning. [Obs.] Bailey.
An example; a pattern or model for imitation. [Obs.] Tyndale.Being ensamples to the flock.
A description or plan of the heavens and the heavenly bodies;the construction of celestial maps, globes, etc.; uranology.
